dataStructure.name: sid.org.tmforum.tip.cbe.policy.fmkspec.PolicyEventSpecAtomic
dataStructure.description:
This is a concrete base class that is used to define the invariant characteristics and behavior (attributes, methods, constraints, and relationships) of a PolicyEventAtomic entity. PolicyEventSpecAtomic entities are stand-alone specifications that define the invariant characteristics and behavior of single (i.e., atomic) PolicyEvents.

This entity is optional
dataStructure.label: PolicyEventSpecAtomic
